
ABOUT
     DSBSu is a Qt frontend to su(1).

INSTALLATION
   Dependencies
     DSBSu depends on devel/qt5-buildtools, devel/qt5-core,
     devel/qt5-linguisttools, devel/qt5-qmake, x11-toolkits/qt5-gui, and
     x11-toolkits/qt5-widgets


   Getting the source code
     # git clone https://github.com/mrclksr/DSBSu.git

   Building and installation
     # cd DSBSu && qmake
     # make && make install

USAGE
     Usage: dsbsu [-m message] [-u user] command
        -m: Message text.
        -u: Username. Default is root.


